    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine condition, showing virtually no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, with all systems functioning exactly as they did when it first left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that is essentially as good as new, requiring absolutely no repairs or cosmetic touch-ups.",
