    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts. The engine currently struggles with consistent performance and requires mechanical attention, while the exterior shows significant wear, including several dents and areas of rust. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn and the electronics are intermittent. It is being sold strictly as-is, and we recommend a full inspection before purchase.",
