    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a sophisticated aesthetic, this model has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting standards for performance and reliability. It offers a balanced synthesis of luxury and dependability, making it an exceptional acquisition for those who demand quality and proven value.",
      "price": 35500.0,
