      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and aesthetic refinement. This unit has been maintained to a rigorous standard, ensuring a driving experience that remains both smooth and responsive. With a comprehensive service history and documented care, it represents a superior acquisition for the discerning driver seeking a balance of prestige and proven performance.",
      "price": 36850.0,
